# Backend API Test Script
# Use with VS Code REST Client extension or any HTTP client

### Root endpoint
GET http://localhost:8080/

### Status Check
GET http://localhost:8080/status

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/test/hello

### Health Check detailed
GET http://localhost:8080/api/test/health

### Swagger UI
GET http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html

### Register new user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nguyen Van Test",
  "email": "test@gmail.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "confirmPassword": "password123",
  "phone": "0901234567",
  "address": "123 Test Street, Ho Chi Minh City",
  "dateOfBirth": "1990-01-01"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@gmail.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get current user (requires JWT token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Check email exists
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/check-email?email=test@gmail.com

### Validate token (requires JWT token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/validate-token
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Get user info (requires JWT token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/user-info
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

